{"tid":2258375,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"調查發現本港整體開心指數為6.16　屬低迷狀態","createTime":"2020-10-26T03:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T04:07:51.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9fd97b6790f7035383c945436f60c45189b62fb5","tid":2258375,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T03:56:47.000Z","msg":"和富社會企業「香港開心D」，委託理工大學護理學院，上月以網上問卷訪問了超過1800人，發現本港整體開心指數為6.16，與去年的分數相若，反映港人仍處於開心指數低迷的狀態。<br />\n<br />\n按年齡組別劃分，12至18歲的開心指數最低，只有5.87分；55歲或以上的開心指數最高，有6.61分。 <br />\n<br />\n港人對10項生活質素滿意度方面，平均只有4.62分，較去年下跌0.05分，反映港人持續受負面的外在環境影響。其中受訪者對政治及社會狀況、信任政府處事程度及政府施政的評分最低，以10分為滿分計算，分別只得3.31、3.04及3.03分。<br />\n<br />\n調查又發現，超過四成半受訪者呈輕度至嚴重抑鬱情緒，較去年增加半成。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2363272\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2363272&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oBFNIXSBonesC3SPsSCGYVE%3D&h=31954c2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2363272</a>"},{"pid":"460c4583bc784dcb20e6ef9065d83c7c83fdc9b7","tid":2258375,"uid":59976,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T03:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i24aPP5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi24aPP5.jpg&h=900e4271&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba50d8e8ad1d3fac3d4df86ff5bf9be80e50fbd8","tid":2258375,"uid":76804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T03:59:06.000Z","msg":"唉我地唔開心唔緊要<br />\n連班細路仔都比支那破壞曬童年真心慘"},{"pid":"64f30b9c4321b388323fbdd6d15079402e8cb5a4","tid":2258375,"uid":290118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T04:00:22.000Z","msg":"是但啦，都係要返工"},{"pid":"40fb638f9e0b532b3236e8d15c3586e2c164bea0","tid":2258375,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T04:01:24.000Z","msg":"個個有得移民走都走啦<br />\n仲點會開心"},{"pid":"28ec9f9b08184e6386492ddac676f0c588b87949","tid":2258375,"uid":49974,"like